		<title>為什麼狗狗散步會忽然「定格」？其實暗藏著這3個小祕密 !</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/09/13/%e7%82%ba%e4%bb%80%e9%ba%bc%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e6%95%a3%e6%ad%a5%e6%9c%83%e5%bf%bd%e7%84%b6%e3%80%8c%e5%ae%9a%e6%a0%bc%e3%80%8d%ef%bc%9f%e5%85%b6%e5%af%a6%e6%9a%97%e8%97%8f%e8%91%97%e9%80%993%e5%80%8b/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sat, 13 Sep 2025 07:14:09 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[時事]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[定格]]></category>
