		<title>為什麼狗狗愛舔人 貓咪卻比較少？背後習性大不同 !</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/09/13/%e7%82%ba%e4%bb%80%e9%ba%bc%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e6%84%9b%e8%88%94%e4%ba%ba-%e8%b2%93%e5%92%aa%e5%8d%bb%e6%af%94%e8%bc%83%e5%b0%91%ef%bc%9f%e8%83%8c%e5%be%8c%e7%bf%92%e6%80%a7%e5%a4%a7%e4%b8%8d%e5%90%8c/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sat, 13 Sep 2025 05:18:47 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[時事]]></category>
